highscores

Class HighScore

  • java.lang.Object
    • highscores.HighScore

  • public class HighScore
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to store an individual highscore. Features of Version 1.0: The constructor with multiple parameters is created to take in all information about the person who achieved the highscore. The accessor methods are all created and no mutator methods are required. Hours spent on this class: 30 minutes.
    Version:
    5.0, June 12, 2014
    Author:
    Salar Hosseini & Sophia Weng
